    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "When Matt Andersen steps on stage, he brings a lifetime of music to every note. The New Brunswick-born powerhouse is known for his soul-stirring voice and heartfelt songs, and his latest album, The Hammer &amp; The Rose, showcases a garden of tender folk and stirring soul that reflects on life’s mos"
